Package org.cloudgraph.store.service

Contains common service provider related interfaces and utilities applicable to most cloud data stores.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AliasMap
    Simple collection managing SQL table aliases
    CommitComparator  
    CreatedCommitComparator
    Comparator which imposes a commit ordering on created objects based on singular relations between the types for the given source and target data objects.
    DeletedCommitComparator
    Comparator which imposes a commit ordering on deleted objects based on singular relations between the types for the given source and target data objects.
    MetricCollector  
    QueryResults
    Encapsulates the collection resulting from query execution along with the Query object itself.

    ToumbstoneRowException
    Exception used for conditions related to toumbstone rows.
